# AI-generated task and baseline docs (dogfooding artifacts in THIS framework repo only).
# Downstream users who install the framework into their own project SHOULD commit their
# /arch:adr output, screen baselines and API baselines normally — these patterns only
# apply to this source repo so we don't accidentally ship test artifacts via npm/npx.
docs/tasks/*/
docs/decisions/*.md
docs/screens/*/
docs/api/*/

# One-shot HTML review artifacts (per Output Format Convention in CLAUDE.md)
docs/tasks/**/*.html
docs/reports/*.html

# OpenCode test results
tests/skill-triggering/opencode-results/
